name: Freddie Mercury
description: Freddie Mercury was a singer, songwriter, music producer, and lead singer of the rock band Queen. Known as one of the greatest singers in the history of rock music, he was known for his glamorous stage personality and four-octave singing. A work by Freddie Mercury in his pixel style designed in 2017. This collection will soon be able to collect the best NFT for future collectors and NFTs from other artists' platforms.
